    <!-- About -->
    <string name="about_title">About eXcap</string>
    <string name="about_message">
        eXcap v2.0.0\n\n
        Professional Network Packet Capture &amp; Analysis Tool\n\n
        Built by eXU CODER\n\n
        Originally based on PCAPdroid by Emanuele Faranda.\n\n
        eXcap uses a local VPN service to capture network traffic\n
        without requiring root access. All data is processed locally\n
        on the device.\n\n
        Features:\n
        - Real-time packet capture via VPN\n
        - HTTP/HTTPS/TCP/UDP/DNS/TLS protocol support\n
        - Deep packet inspection with nDPI\n
        - Per-app traffic monitoring and filtering\n
        - TLS decryption via CA certificate\n
        - PCAP/PCAPng export\n
        - Material Design 3 UI with Jetpack Compose\n\n
        License: GNU General Public License v3.0
    </string>

